## Summary of Key Design System Elements

**Color Palette:**
- Primary backgrounds are warm creams/near-whites (light: #FAF9F6) and very dark (dark: #0C0C0C)
- Accent colors use amber (#D4A853) and sage green (#8A9E7A)
